messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Remove phone number +12453344098 from my contact
Could you please provide the unique identifier (person_id) for the contact entry that you would like to modify?
I don't have that information, sorry.

No problem! Let's start by identifying the contact you want to remove. Could you please provide the name or any other details (like another phone number) associated with the contact? This will help me find the right entry for you.
I only have the phone number +12453344098.

Let me look up the contact based on the phone number +12453344098 to get the person_id for removal. Please hold on for a moment. 

However, I currently don't have the ability to look up contacts directly. If you could provide me with the details of your contacts, I may be able to assist you better. Do you need help with anything else?
No worries, that's all I got.

If you only have the phone number and no other information to identify the contact, I won't be able to remove it without the unique identifier (person_id). 

Please check your contacts to see if there's additional information about that entry. If you find any other details, just let me know, and I can help you from there!
